precis:
Amendments to the MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 removing Townsend
Lake, Heming Lake, Wapun Lake & South Lake from the list of lakes in
which no fishing is allowed, adding zebra mussels to the schedule of
prohibited species, and removing the ban on dip netting in Natural Brook
Trout Waters.
